@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "James Moon's Profile";
}
<div class="home" id="home">
    <div id="test" class="adminpanel" hidden>
        <input type="button" value="Pop Titles" name="PopTitles" onclick="PopTitles()" />
    </div>
    <video autoplay muted loop id="myVideo">
        <source src="~/img/animation.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="titletext">
        <p>
            <!-- Welcome to James Moon's Portfolio -->
            Test
        </p>
    </div>
    <p class="navtext navtext-right" id="navtext-right">Contact Me</p>
    <p class="navtext navtext-left" id="navtext-left">About Me</p>
    <p class="navtext navtext-bottom" id="navtext-bottom">My Projects</p>
    <div class="leftButton justify-content-between" id="leftbutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-left" id="leftarrow"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="rightButton justify-content-between" id="rightbutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-right" id="rightarrow"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="bottomButton justify-content-between" id="bottombutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-bottom" id="bottomarrow"></i>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="rightPage">
    <div class="contentbox d-flex justify-content-between">
        <div class="leftcontent">
            <p class="contenttitle display-4 text-center">
                Contact Me
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="comments">
            <p>Feel free to leave a comment with your thoughts on my profile. Please do not leave any personal details here as it is open to the public.</p>
            <div class="entercomment justify-content-end" id="entercomment">
                <div class="commentAuthor">
                    <label for="author">Author</label>
                    <input type="text" maxlength="25" id="author" />
                </div>
                <div class="commentString">
                    <label for="comment">Your Comment</label>
                    <input type="text" maxlength="500" id="comment" />
                </div>
                <input type="button" id="submitComment" title="Send" value="Send" />
            </div>
            <hr />
            <div class="allcomments justify-content-end" id="allcomments">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="leftButton justify-content-between" id="leftbutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-left" id="leftarrow"></i>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="leftPage">
    <div class="contentbox">
        <p class="contenttitle display-4 text-center">
            About Me
        </p>
        <p class="contenttext p-1">My name is James Moon, I am a Web developer with experience with a vast variety of programming and design languages skills. I am a passionate designer of webpages and applications, and practice animation and film editing on the side. I enjoy the occasianal game and have made a few myself. One of my other passions is discovering and reviving old technology, including Desktops, applications, handhelds, consoles and servers. I'm a fan of emulation and combining the software and hardware side of development is I am passionate about.</p>
        <p class="contenttext p-1">In terms of who I really am as a person, I come from a small area called Giants Creek, 2 hours north-west of Newcastle on a farm. Learning technology was very restricted where I was from due to lack of teaching knowledge (The main focus was Agriculture and Industrial Trade). University opened my mind to different styles never imagined and I continue to self-teach to this day.</p>
        <p class="contenttext p-1" style="padding-right: 50%;">Feel free to grab any details from my "Contact Me" page located to the right of the home page. Check out some of my work on the page below home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rightButton justify-content-between" id="rightbutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-right" id="rightarrow"></i>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bottomPage">
    <div class="contentboxlong">
        <p class="contenttitle display-4 text-center">
            My Projects
        </p>
        <p class="contenttext p-1">I have to be clear. Most of my projects are protected under university or work guidelines, but the ones I can show here are freely developed by James as "personal projects". Here is a list of just some of them:</p>
        <div class="projects">
            <div class="project">
                <div class="leftproject">
                    <h1>How-To Houdini</h1>
                    <p>How-To Houdini started as a university project that I later cleaned up and polished to be an informative website for people just starting to use the 3D progressive animation software Houdini. The website featured videos and a simple chatbot that could be of assistance to the user on the site.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rightproject">
                    <img class="projectimage" src="~/img/howtohoudini.PNG" alt="HowToHoudiniHomepage" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <div class="leftproject">
                    <h1>"Complexica" Animation</h1>
                    <p>The hurdles of learning Houdini was the making of this animation. All models and character were built and animated by myself in Houdini.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rightproject">
                    <img class="projectimage" src="~/img/complexica.png" alt="Complexica" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <p class="absolutecenter">More to come in the future....</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="topButton justify-content-between" id="topbutton">
        <i class="arrow arrow-top" id="toparrow"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer">
        <p class="shadowdemon">You ever heard of the Konami code?</p>
    </div>
</div>

@section scripts {
    <script type="text/javascript">
        //console.log(ViewBag.CommentID + ", " + ViewBag.CommentAuthor + ", " + ViewBag.CommentString + ", " + ViewBag.CommentDate);

        $(document).ready(function () {
            GetComments();
        });

        document.getElementById("submitComment").onclick = function () {
            var author = document.getElementById("author").value;
            var comment = document.getElementById("comment").value;
            $.ajax({
                url: '@Url.Action("StoreComment", "Home")',
                data: { 'author': author, 'comment': comment },
                success: function (data) {
                    GetComments();
                },
                error: function (request, status, error) {
                    alert(request.responseText.split("\n")[0]);
                }
            });
        };

        function GetComments() {
            const options = {
                year: 'numeric',
                month: '2-digit',
                day: '2-digit',
                hour: '2-digit',
                minute: '2-digit',
                hour12: false,
                timeZone: 'Australia/Sydney'
            };
            $.ajax({
                url: '@Url.Action("GetComments", "Home")',
                success: function (data) {
                    var allComments = "";
                    for (let i = data.length - 1; i > -1; i--) {
                        var comment = data[i];
                        allComments += "<div class='comment'><div class='comment-meta'><span class='comment-author'>" + comment["commentAuthor"] + "</span><span class='comment-date'>" + comment["commentDate"] + "</span></div><div class='comment-text'><p'>" + comment["commentString"] + "</p></div></div>";
                    }
                    document.getElementById("allcomments").innerHTML = allComments;
                },
                error: function (request, status, error) {
                    alert(request.responseText.split("\n")[0]);
                }
            });
        }

        let active = '';
        $('.rightButton').click(function () {
            $('.home').toggleClass('homeVisibility');
            if (active == '') {
                active = 'right';
                $('.rightPage').toggleClass('activeRight');
            }
            else if (active == 'left') {
                active = '';
                $('.leftPage').toggleClass('activeLeft');
            }
            //console.log(active);
        });
        $('.leftButton').click(function () {
            $('.home').toggleClass('homeVisibility');
            if (active == '') {
                active = 'left';
                $('.leftPage').toggleClass('activeLeft');
            }
            else if (active == 'right') {
                active = '';
                $('.rightPage').toggleClass('activeRight');
            }
            //console.log(active);
        });
        $('.bottomButton').click(function () {
            $('.home').toggleClass('homeVisibility');
            if (active == '') {
                active = 'bottom';
                $('.bottomPage').toggleClass('activeBottom');
                $('.bottomPage').toggleClass('scrollable');
            }
            else if (active == 'top') {
                active = '';
                $('.topPage').toggleClass('activetop');
            }
            //console.log(active);
        });
        $('.topButton').click(function () {
            $('.home').toggleClass('homeVisibility');
            if (active == '') {
                active = 'top';
                $('.topPage').toggleClass('activeTop');
            }
            else if (active == 'bottom') {
                active = '';
                $('.bottomPage').toggleClass('activeBottom');
                $('.bottomPage').toggleClass('scrollable');
            }
            //console.log(active);
        });

        const leftButton = document.getElementById('leftbutton');
        const rightButton = document.getElementById('rightbutton');
        const bottomButton = document.getElementById('bottombutton');
        const leftArrow = document.getElementById('leftarrow');
        const rightArrow = document.getElementById('rightarrow');
        const bottomArrow = document.getElementById('bottomarrow');

        leftButton.addEventListener('mouseover', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-left').toggleClass('activenavtext-left');
        });
        rightButton.addEventListener('mouseover', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-right').toggleClass('activenavtext-right');
        });
        bottomButton.addEventListener('mouseover', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-bottom').toggleClass('activenavtext-bottom');
        });

        leftButton.addEventListener('mouseout', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-left').toggleClass('activenavtext-left');
        });
        rightButton.addEventListener('mouseout', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-right').toggleClass('activenavtext-right');
        });
        bottomButton.addEventListener('mouseout', function handleMouseOver() {
            $('.navtext-bottom').toggleClass('activenavtext-bottom');
        });

        function PopTitles() {
            $('.navtext-right').toggleClass('activenavtext-right');
            $('.navtext-bottom').toggleClass('activenavtext-bottom');
            $('.navtext-left').toggleClass('activenavtext-left');
        }
    </script>
}